At the same time, the revenue of AvtoVAZ PJSC decreased by 20.8% to 38.417 billion rubles. Such data follow from the IFRS statements published by the company. Lada sales amounted to 56,879 units, or 17% less compared to the same period in 2015. The production of cars at AvtoVAZ (Lada, Renault, Nissan, Datsun) also decreased - by 34% compared to the 1st quarter of 2015 to 96 498 cars.